------------------------------

UPDATED:

Alot has been changed:

- New Skybox
- Brighter
- Lowered walls and added smoother brushes
- Removed pink neons completely
- A few other things

note: the thumbnail screenshots look correct, the full screenshots are somehow linked back to the old version (pink neons).

------------------------------

This is the first release I'm really proud of.

It took me about 7 hours to create (and about the same to upload it)

There are 24 protected spawn points.

Beautiful textures and smooth brushes included ;)

I hope you enjoy this release and provide me with your feedback.
